  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "Currently we check deposit signatures [one-by-one](https://github.com/ConsenSys/teku/blob/70e2d323748f668af288c89d9c5813bab28b8df1/ethereum/spec/src/main/java/tech/pegasys/teku/spec/logic/common/block/AbstractBlockProcessor.java#L654) when processing new deposits. Since there are up to 16 deposits per block we could likely save some time by batch verifying them together. We don't need to know which one fails (if any) as the whole block is invalid if any signature is invalid.\r\n",
